{"tid":1825830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來好多老人搞唔清生果金同長者津貼，林鄭加長津只得4%老人受惠","createTime":"2020-01-15T15:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T16:40:34.000Z","uid":36901,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6739d77569936f994139f858c8d648c8e1afd6e8","tid":1825830,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"話說今日同個Uncle 食飯，傾開林鄭個乜柒民生措施<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />uncle<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:Uncle,林鄭早兩日搞左個十大措施，你地有冇份呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔清楚，老婆有兩蚊車，同埋好似話加老人金到3500蚊，如果兩個加埋都有7000蚊，不過唔知幾時有錢。不過你地後生仔就陰公d，好似乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:都預左，條柒婆早就放棄左我地，最慘係d 00後，未出黎社會已經被迫害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:所以佢而家要派錢俾我地D老野， 掩口費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:其實你地都唔係好老，係呢Uncle你大定我老豆大?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我今年71歲，應該你老豆大d，上年先有有千幾蚊老人金<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔止咁少下話，應該有2600幾架喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔係喎，得1300咋喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:咁你個應該係生果金黎，加到3500蚊個係長者津貼先有架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:下唔係嘛，唔係話加老人金，放寬到60歲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻連我都俾佢搞亂左，於是即刻上網check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:Uncle，你搞錯喇，生果金冇得加架，同埋得2蚊車放寬到60咋，生果金冇呀，都係要等70先有1300蚊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我仲以為兩公婆有7000蚊，而家即係乜都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:已經好過我架喇，你地有兩蚊車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:呢個政府真係正仆街，後生既就打，老既就呃，林鄭快撚d死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我跟手上社會福利署個網睇下，原來得唔夠5萬個普通長者津貼有得加錢，當香港有120萬老人，即係得4%有得加錢，96%老人空歡喜一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99e512008e4a38d93753faae79a75c1f3645589","tid":1825830,"uid":255536,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"是但啦 拎唔到仲好<br />\n等陣廢老多個錢又去公園助養活家禽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167b37870afdd4a7ccf66cb49a8c997288c5c1d7","tid":1825830,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6739d77569936f994139f858c8d648c8e1afd6e8","tid":1825830,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"話說今日同個Uncle 食飯，傾開林鄭個乜柒民生措施<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />uncle<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:Uncle,林鄭早兩日搞左個十大措施，你地有冇份呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔清楚，老婆有兩蚊車，同埋好似話加老人金到3500蚊，如果兩個加埋都有7000蚊，不過唔知幾時有錢。不過你地後生仔就陰公d，好似乜都冇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:都預左，條柒婆早就放棄左我地，最慘係d 00後，未出黎社會已經被迫害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:所以佢而家要派錢俾我地D老野， 掩口費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:其實你地都唔係好老，係呢Uncle你大定我老豆大?